sub_title: Policy Coordinator North Africa | North Africa and Middle East Department | Ministry of Foreign Affairs of The Netherlands
summary: Generalist profile and solid experience at Dutch missions abroad. I speak several  languages and have a wide range of interests. My expertise covers the fields of Political Affairs, Latin America, European Affairs, as well as Economic Diplomacy. My experience includes working at Netherlands missions in Mexico, Brussels and Paris, at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and the Ministry of Economic Affairs.
